<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
      <title>Customer Home - Engineered Assets</title>
      <meta name="description" content="Explore and manage engineering tools, place orders, view your cart, and update your profile seamlessly.">
      <link rel='stylesheet' href='/styles/bootstrap.min.css' />
      <link rel='stylesheet' href='/styles/style.css' />
      <script src="/js/jquery-2.2.0.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
      <style>
body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #D8D2C2; 
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .center {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .navbar-inverse .nav > li > a {
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-inverse .nav > li > a:hover {
            color: #ffd700; 
        }

        .navbar-inverse .navbar-brand {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-inverse .navbar-brand:hover {
            color: #ffd700;
        }

        .navbar-inverse .nav i {
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .navbar-inverse {
            background-color: #343a40; 
            border: none;
        }
    </style>

    <div>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
            <a class="navbar-brand">Engineering Assets</a>
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
      <li><a href="/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Customer Home Page</a></li>
      <li><a href="/userprofile"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Profile</a></li>
      <li><a href="/UserEquipments"><i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i> Equipments</a></li>
      <li><a href="/cart"><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Cart</a></li>
      <li><a href="/order"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Orders</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right" style="padding-right: 30px;">
                <li><a href="/"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="center">
      <h1>Welcome, Customer {{ name }}</h1>
      <p>Manage your profile, explore our equipment inventory, track your orders, and manage your cart for a seamless experience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><a href="/userprofile">Your Profile</a></h2>
      <p>Access and update your personal details, such as contact information and preferences, to keep your account up to date.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><a href="/UserEquipments">Explore Equipments</a></h2>
      <p>Discover a wide range of engineering tools and assets, categorized for easy browsing. From power tools to measurement instruments, find everything you need for your projects.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><a href="/cart">Review Your Cart</a></h2>
      <p>Ensure you have everything you need before checkout. Adjust quantities, remove items, or proceed to purchase your selected tools.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2><a href="/order">Track Your Orders</a></h2>
      <p>Stay informed about the status of your placed orders, including current processing stages and estimated delivery times.</p>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>